data.description: Five bedrooms and a home office in North Meridian’s Bridge Tower. Located on a quarter-acre corner lot this custom Tresidio home is close to schools, parks, grocery stores and restaurants. The lot borders a common area in the back yard. Inside and out this home has ample room for a family to thrive. The formal dining room / office is in addition to the five bedrooms. The oversized three car garage has an extended third bay with easy backyard access through a roll up utility door. The kitchen includes a walk-in pantry, granite countertops, dual ovens, and an oversize gas cooktop. The primary bedroom and guest suite are both on the ground floor. The primary bedroom includes direct patio access, an oversized walk-in shower and large walk-in closet. The house and back patio are wired with surround sound. The primary bedroom and all bathrooms are fully insulated for noise reduction. The carpet is new. Bridge Tower offers many family friendly amenities with swimming pools, play grounds, and walking paths.
